	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=13785">Implementing Original Music for Nintendo &amp; Sega Game Dev</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320">Moderators</a></p>

